Package: jirc
Version: 1.0-1
Architecture: all
Maintainer: Kees Cook <kees@debian.org>
Installed-Size: 96
Depends: perl, libconfig-simple-perl, libxml-stream-perl, libpoe-component-irc-perl, libfilter-template-perl, libpoe-component-jabber-perl (>= 3.00-1), libpoe-filter-xml-perl, libnet-jabber-perl
Recommends: libnet-ssleay-perl
Section: perl
Priority: optional
Homepage: http://outflux.net/software/pkgs/jirc-bridge/
Description: an IRC to Jabber bridge bot
 The jirc bot logs into an IRC channel and a Jabber conference room.  It will
 relay conversations between the two rooms, identifying each of the speakers
 in braces.  Actions are forwarded as well.
